{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were transports of-- of army, German Army, flowing through the tracks, and therefore we had to be sidetracked on occasion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we probably did not make good time in getting to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The distance couldn't have been that great, but it took us many, many days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Gross-Rosen, we were standing on the Appellplatz, stripped totally, no clothes, were ordered to run towards the showers, toward the delousing facility.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We entered the showers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we needed to be clean for whatever would happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the shower-- after we were showered, we were given some piece of clothing, just like one piece of clothing, whatever it happened to be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was either a shirt or a jacket or-- or pants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is what you got, you got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was your-- your clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I remember getting some kind of a gown, which was long, and this was my clothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] If I ever got a-- a-- another striped outfit, I don't recall that, whether there was enough time for me to get that or not.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I somehow recall that I wound up on the transport with just that one piece of clothing that I had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were in Gross-Rosen itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once we came out of the showers, we faced a battery of-- of guards who were giving us a crew cut.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the crew cut, they-- the guards attempted to shave our-- shave a 2-inch strip from front to back on the head.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And evidently, this was designed so to keep us from being able to flee from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As the guards were shaving that 2-inch inch strip from front to back, they would spit on our heads to make that shaving process possible.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
